::DarkMouse::

She came around, barely.  She noticed that she was inside something, 
but couldn't tell what or where. She then fell into darkness.  Her 
body, healling quickly.  The leaking had stopped and her internal 
injuries would soon be healed. 


--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, minime_316@h... wrote:
> Starscream passed over the flames and look down at the mouse, movin 
> and twitching. It was still alive, and Starscream did not have it 
in 
> him to fight a helpless bot. He watched the fire on her die down, 
and 
> than placed her in the cockpit and sealed it tight, chaining her to 
> the seat. He would take her back to KitKat, and she would decide 
what 
> to do with her. Maybe she knew where Megatron was. He would stop by 
> the base, put this rodent in custody, and than go and help Drillbit 
> defeat Inferno. He blasted of towards the base.
